OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMan sentenced to death for 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FJapan anime studio fire    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Japanese man has been sentenced to   
OL,6, death for an arson attack at a Kyoto   
OL,7, animation studio in 2019 which killed  
OL,8, 36 people and injured dozens more.     
OL,10,FThe incident, one of Japan's deadliest 
OL,11,Fin recent decades, killed mostly young 
OL,12,Fartists and shocked the anime world.   
OL,14,FShinji Aoba, 45, pleaded guilty to the 
OL,15,Fattack but his lawyers had sought a    
OL,16,Flighter sentence on grounds of "mental 
OL,17,Fincompetence".                         
OL,19,FJudges rejected this however, ruling   
OL,20,Fthat Aoba knew what he was doing.      
